Usage: set_socv_constraint_config [-help] [-hold_folding <float>]
                                  -libs <string>
                                  [-nochange_hold_folding <float>]
                                  [-nochange_setup_folding <float>]
                                  [-setup_folding <float>]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-hold_folding <float>               # Amount of additional sigma units added on
                                    # top of the existing nominal hold value
                                    # (float, optional, min=-100, max=100)
-libs <string>                      # List of library names (not library paths)
                                    # or collection object (string, required)
-nochange_hold_folding <float>      # Amount of additional sigma units added on
                                    # top of the existing nominal hold value
                                    # for no-change timing arcs
                                    # (float, optional, min=-100, max=100)
-nochange_setup_folding <float>     # Amount of additional sigma units added on
                                    # top of the existing nominal setup value
                                    # for no-change timing arcs
                                    # (float, optional, min=-100, max=100)
-setup_folding <float>              # Amount of additional sigma units added on
                                    # top of the existing nominal setup value
                                    # (float, optional, min=-100, max=100)